import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';

class BasementRenovationsInMarkham extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovations In Markham</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovations in Markham" />
        <div className="container">
          <p>Offering an experienced and quality basement renovation service in Markham, AGM Basements are specialists in the field. Having completed over 250 basements in the area, we are able to offer affordable and desirable solutions for bringing your space to life.</p>

          <h3>Basement renovations that meet your needs</h3>

          <p>We complete projects for all kinds of homes in need of basement renovations, regardless of size, age or stature. At AGM, we are always committed to meeting the brief within the set timeframe and budgetary requirements so that you go away happy. To achieve those ends, our dedicated designers and tradesmen work side by side with you to ensure your new basement meets all your criteria.</p>

          <p>Basement finishing isn’t always an easy job, as it requires an experienced team to give you the basement you want. Having excelled in the field for the past 18 years, AGM is proud to offer unparalleled service in the Markham area with excellent client recommendations. We never walk away from a job until the client is satisfied.</p>

          <p>Our team can ensure your custom design needs are met with no job being too big for us to handle or too small for our time. We have the means and ability to transform any basement into a space you will be proud to show off.</p>

          <p>Here are just some of the projects we can assist with transforming your basement into:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Kitchens</li>
            <li>Bars</li>
            <li>Fireplaces</li>
            <li>Saunas</li>
            <li>Gym or workout spaces</li>
            <li>Wine cellars</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>The basement renovation company you can trust</h3>

          <p>When looking for someone you can trust to complete your basement remodelling, it's good to know that AGM are that trustworthy company. We always ensure 100% satisfaction with a completed interior project and welcome potential clients to attend one of our many finishing showcases and open houses for you to see how our basements look for yourself - the quality has to be seen to be believed!</p>

          <p>Clients who find themselves satisfied with our services often praise the new living area we have provided for them, the additional room, the ability to get around zoning codes and the value that has been added to their property.</p>

          <h3>Satisfaction guaranteed</h3>

          <p>Your satisfaction and safety remain our number one priority and as such we ensure all our products are finished to the highest safety standards, including our total seal for mould and rust, our signature water seal, as well as our total seal for radon, ensuring that your basement will not only look good and be safe but stay this way.</p>

          <p>Our customer guarantee means that we are dedicated to our client’s satisfaction, so you don’t pay a penny until you’re happy with the finished project. What's more, our tradesmen are of the highest standard who prioritise completing your job on time. If we don't, you have our word that we will pay you if the project is late! We are proud to offer a free estimate service - please give us a call today to have a chat about your dream basement and how we can help.</p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationsInMarkham;
